<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cloth-n">cloth <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /klɒθ/    美 /klɔːθ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 布；布料：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cut the coat according to the cloth.
量体裁衣。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’d better wrap it in a piece of clean cloth.
你最好用一块干净的布将它包好。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] （一块）布：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They handed each of us a hot wet cloth to wipe our hands.
他们递给我们每个人一块温热的湿布擦手。</p></div></div>